commit_message:
dpeak 2.0.1

better data processing & prediction: (1) common peak shape; (2) better
initialization; (3) utilization of motif information.

Update README.md

Incorporate description for dPeak

dpeakRead now accepts GRanges object

Added a conditional that coerces peakfile to a data.frame if it is a GRanges object.  Otherwise, it is assumed that peakfile is a file with first three columns as chr, start, end.
